data.description: Searching for an in-law suite? This 4 bedroom, 3 bathroom home in the master planned community of Waterset provides the solution. The in-law suite offers the perfect blend of comfort, style, and functionality with a versatile space featuring a bedroom, full bathroom and an additional flex/living room with a sink, counter space and a full size refrigerator. The suite is ideal for guests or extended family, or can be used as a home office or game room. The primary bedroom is complete with an ensuite bathroom for ultimate privacy. Granite countertops, stainless steel appliances and an island are featured in the kitchen and a convenient laundry room adds a touch of practicality. On the screened-in lanai you'll find a stand alone hot tub connected to an independent electrical breaker box with room for connecting your future outdoor kitchen or other enhancement requiring power.  In this highly sought-after Waterset community, you'll have access to an array of amenities including clubhouses, a fitness center, parks, trails, and community pools. This community provides more than just a home; it provides a lifestyle. Don't miss your opportunity, schedule a showing today.
